title: Ep 48: When Did Humility Become a Bad Thing?
description: In this episode I explore humility - from it's roots in religion to the apparent lack of it today in popular culture. Why do people hate Anne Hathaway? And why does Tyler Oakley make me sad inside? See for yourself https://www.youtube.com/user/tyleroakley
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
